306
00:15:15,021 --> 00:15:16,532
Fishman.

307
00:15:16,533 --> 00:15:18,355
Son prénom est Melvin.

308
00:15:18,356 --> 00:15:20,884
Carlo s'appelle Melvin Fishman ?

309
00:15:20,885 --> 00:15:23,263
Il vient de l'Ohio,

310
